{"tid":19541,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"開左個二手Gaming gear FB group","createTime":"2016-12-03T00:19:54.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T02:30:50.000Z","uid":33940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"470598e8872c4b2b7e788b939d9ba8b42bc9d06c","tid":19541,"uid":33940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T00:19:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/1848564362094331/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F1848564362094331%2F&d=qkncW4ahWQk%2FJA9l97O%2FUpkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=55669765\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/1848564362094331/</a><br />\n<br />\n眼見無地方係專for人賣gaming gear, 所以開左個FB group, 希望group到對呢樣野有興趣既人, 日後想買/賣都起碼有個地方去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79aa8c98c955f9d96b9a375a6e67295ddda72c88","tid":19541,"uid":33940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T01:35:07.000Z","msg":"pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaa30310e5a73274c8c54d92851cfca3c3b6907","tid":19541,"uid":33940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:13:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e9f0db7e8ac2f209081cce0738221d5bb59ec06","tid":19541,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:25:16.000Z","msg":"點解唔用dcfever?"},{"pid":"71cb6f3a3df876c2fa91c31adbe1907921df7aee","tid":19541,"uid":33940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:47:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解唔用dcfever?</blockquote><br />\n你想買/賣gaming mouse/keyboard 會唔會第一時間諗到去dcfever先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 宜家就係無一個咁樣既地方 所以先想開呢個group集中番 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n同埋賣二手野用facebook應該都方便過dcfever 起碼人地出post你會見到 dcfever就要你特登search某個brand/某件product"},{"pid":"905d7b1b2ab